'''Rojen Barnas''' is the [[pen name]] of '''Mehmet Gemici''' (born 1945), a contemporary [[Kurdish people|Kurdish]] poet and writer. He was born in the [[Diyarbakır]] region in south-eastern [[Turkey]].  He became active in Kurdish politics in the 1970s. He has made his home in [[Sweden]] since 1981. He started publishing a Kurdish magazine called ''{{ill|Tîrêj|ku|Tîrêj (kovar)}}'' in the 1970s. He has also published articles in other Kurdish journals such as ''{{ill|Hêvî|ku|Hêvî (kovar)}}'' and ''{{ill|Nûdem|ku|Nûdem (kovar)}}''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.immi.se/kultur/authors/kurder/gemici.htm|title=Mehmet Gemici, Invandrade Författare|website=www.immi.se}}</ref>

